{
  "stem": "14737.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the town crier went from corner to corner and on a drum-- he had only one hand.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Feather-- was announcing about Jews, and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Jews had to put on star, everyone had to make a star by tomorrow, yellow star.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everyone has to paint on the house a big Magen David-- what do you call it-- a Magen David star.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jews couldn't get any more rations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so it's going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How shall I describe you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The situation in Dovhoje was very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But here, you cannot run away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You cannot go-- what's to go, where to go?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father and my sister-- people are asking me in Dovhoje, my name is Zoli, what's going to happen?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How is it going to be?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "By the curfew was-- we cannot go out only from 8 till 6 o'clock-- only what we must to buy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And gendarmes are enforcing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And who wants to see a gendarme?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because he's hitting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He's-- So I find myself in a situation like this-- why didn't I run away?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Why didn't I go away?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I'm here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My father is sad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And what can you do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My sister-- not too much food already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But in our house, it's still a little bit food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I decided what's going to be is going to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going to beat the rest of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now I'm a strong man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll work some place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What's going to happen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But so far, nothing's happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't see even one German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's no Germans here, Hungarians, but harsh, and every day new.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So next day comes out every Jewish household has to bring to the synagogue all his belongings-- not furniture, like linens, linens.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So people bundled up whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were poor people.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
